headline: Ventas: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The results topped Wall Street expectations. The Chicago-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $406.2 million, or 88 cents per share, in the period. The average estimate of five analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of 87 cents per share.
